Invocation Name: metronome
Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill is an acoustical metronome that plays a regular drumbeat. You can use it to time yourself or to help you keep the beat while practicing music. You can pick any rate between 40 and 199 beats per minute. It will play the beats until you say 'Alexa, stop'. If you want more, you can ask it to resume, or switch to a new rate.
